            <div>
              <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/%E6%B3%A1%E9%A6%8D/@34.2110869,108.8344808,12z/data=!3m1!4b1?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDcwOC4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D" 
                 target="_blank" 
                 rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                 style="color: #C49E3A; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;">
                 Yangrou paomo
              </a>
              — Tear your own flatbread into a bowl of rich lamb broth.
            </div>
          </li>
