          <span style="margin-left: auto; background: #EDEAE0; color: #6c757d; padding: 0.1rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 500;">5 spots</span>
        </div>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
