            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start; color: #4a4a4a; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">
            <span style="color: #C49E3A; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>
            <div>
              <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/%E4%B8%B2%E4%B8%B2%E9%A6%99/@30.6063074,104.1095242,15z/data=!3m1!4b1?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDcwOC4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D" 
                 target="_blank" 
                 rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                 style="color: #C49E3A; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;">
                 Chuanchuan skewers
              </a>
              — Bamboo sticks of meat and veg, cooked in a bubbling pot.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start; color: #4a4a4a; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">
            <span style="color: #C49E3A; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">▸</span>
            <div>
              <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kuanzhai+Alley+Chengdu" 
